metadata.name: Angel / Whore
metadata.description:
The Mannequin: Molded in our image and yet their perfectly formed lithe bodies with pert breasts and flawless skin serve to remind us of a perfect vision of an unattainable standard. A reminder of the shallowness of the pursuit of beauty which is only ever skin deep. And yet even these statuesque angel, whore, goddesses beauty fades. 
What becomes of the discarded? 
These are the Mannequeens.

An experiment in Photographic Editing and Digital Ai Art by accomplished Australian Artist AprilYFU.
